snippet.title: YARG Setlist: Wave 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Wave 3 is here! Check out 6 new songs featuring Atomic Guava, Frostbitt, Krilloan, Practically People, Sweet Bike, and Thanks! I Hate It available now through the launcher! Just download/update the setlist and the songs will automatically be included in your library when you launch YARG.

Download the YARG Launcher here: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARC-Launcher/releases 

If you're a developer, artist, or band and are interested in contributing to YARG, feel free to join us on Discord, GitHub, or contact us via our email. We are 100% open source and always welcome anyone who wants to contribute!

Interested in getting your music added to the official YARG setlist or a DLC pack? Reach out to yargchartingteam@gmail.com and we'll get back to you as soon as possible!
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Website: https://yarg.in/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/yarg
GitHub: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARG
